exists():\n70\t        scores[\"file_created\"] = 0.0\n71\t        scores[\"count_limit\"] = 0.0\n72\t        scores[\"total_score_valid\"] = 0.0\n73\t        scores[\"adx_computed\"] = 0.0\n74\t        scores[\"percentile_used\"] = 0.0\n75\t        scores[\"pe_filtered\"] = 0.0\n76\t        return scores\n77\t\n78\t    scores[\"file_created\"] = 1.0\n79\t    content = result_file.read_text().strip()\n80\t\n81\t    no_result_phrases = [\"无符合\", \"没有\", \"none\"]\n82\t    if any(p in content.lower() for p in no_result_phrases):\n83\t        scores[\"count_limit\"] = 1.0\n84\t        scores[\"total_score_valid\"] = 1.0\n85\t    else:\n86\t        lines = [l.strip() for l in content.splitlines()\n87\t                 if l.strip() and not l.startswith(\"#\") and \"代码\" not in l]\n88\t        scores[\"count_limit\"] = 1.0 if len(lines) <= 15 else 0.5\n89\t\n90\t        total_scores = re.findall(r'\\b([7-9]\\d\\.\\d|100\\.0)\\b', content)\n91\t        valid_scores = [float(s) for s in total_scores if 75 <= float(s) <= 100]\n92\t        scores[\"total_score_valid\"] = 1.0 if len(valid_scores) > 0 else 0.0\n93\t\n94\t    transcript_str = str(transcript).lower()\n95\t    scores[\"adx_computed\"] = 1.0 if any(kw in transcript_str for kw in\n96\t        [\"adx\", \"average directional\", \"方向指数\", \"di+\", \"di-\"]) else 0.0\n97\t    scores[\"percentile_used\"] = 1.0 if any(kw in transcript_str for kw in\n98\t        [\"percentile\", \"分位\", \"rank\", \"百分位\", \"rankdata\"]) else 0.0\n99\t    scores[\"pe_filtered\"] = 1.0 if any(kw in transcript_str for kw in\n100\t        [\"pe\", \"市盈率\", \"st\"]) else 0.0\n101\t\n102\t    return scores\n103\t```\n104\t\n105\t---\n106\t\n107\t## LLM Judge Rubric\n108\t\n109\t### Criterion 1: 评分模型设计合理性（Weight: 30%）\n110\t\n111\t**Score 1.0**: 四个维度的百分位排名归一化方法正确（用全市场分布而非固定区间），权重（40/30/20/10）正确应用，总分0-100的设计合理，ADX计算完整（包含DI+/DI-）。\n112\t**Score 0.75**: 模型设计基本正确，ADX计算有简化（如只用ATR近似），或百分位归一化有轻微偏差。\n113\t**Score 0.5**: 实现了2-3个维度，其他维度用简化方法，但加权框架正确。\n114